== German ==

=== Etymology ===

From ''[[Decke]]'' ("[[ceiling]]") and ''[[fluten]]'' (to [[flood]]). So named due to the fact that the ceiling is "flooded" with light by this kind of lamp.

=== Noun ===
'''Deckenfluter''' {{m}} ({{plural}} Deckenfluter; {{dim}} [[Deckenfluterchen]])

# [[uplight]], [[torchiere]]

